{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id8fbbe307-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2429a–1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2429a–1"},"text":"§ 2429a–1.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Annual report on nuclear transfer activities","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Beginning with the fiscal year 1983 and for each fiscal year thereafter, the President shall prepare and transmit to the Congress, as part of the presentation materials for foreign assistance programs proposed for that fiscal year, a classified report describing the nuclear programs and related activities of any country for which a waiver of section 2799aa or 2799aa–1 of this title is in effect, including an assessment of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id8fbbe308-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2429a–1/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the extent and effectiveness of International Atomic Energy Agency safeguards at that country’s nuclear facilities; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id8fbbe309-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s2429a–1/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the capability, actions, and intentions of the government of that country with respect to the manufacture or acquisition of a nuclear explosive device.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id8fbbe30a-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/113/tVII/s735"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–113, title VII, § 735","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-12-29"},"text":"Dec. 29, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/1561"},"text":"95 Stat. 1561","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/236/tVIII/s826/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–236, title VIII, § 826(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-04-30"},"text":"Apr. 30, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/519"},"text":"108 Stat. 519","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id8fbbe30b-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id8fbbe30c-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id8fbbe30d-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the International Security and Development Cooperation Act of 1981, and not as part of the Foreign Assistance Act of 1961 which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id8fbbe30e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1994—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/236"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–236","children":[],"tail":" substituted “section 2799aa or 2799aa–1” for “section 2429 or 2429a”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id8fbbe30f-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and 